-- Rostelecom May Extend CEO’s Contract Five Years, Kommersant Says
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2011-12-22T04:41:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-22/rostelecom-may-extend-ceo-s-contract-five-years-kommersant-says.html
OAO Rostelecom ,  Russia ’s state
telecoms holding, may extend Chief Executive Officer Alexander
Provotorov’s contract for five more years,  Kommersant  reported.  The CEO’s salary may be tripled to 3.1 million rubles
($98,000) per month, the Moscow-based newspaper reported today,
citing company documents.  To contact the reporter on this story:
